ongoing and growing demand for featurerich consumer products chipmakers are challenged to mass produce highly sophisticated devices to keep pace and meet challenging production requirements semiconductor manufacturers will need to invest in highly versatile and reliable wafer fabrication equipment lam’s recent merger with novellus systems inc has created a broad portfolio of complementary product capabilities that includes lam’s leadership in etch and singlewafer clean and novellus’ leadership in thin film deposition and photoresist strip the combined company is well positioned to lead the global semiconductor industry through the next critical technology transitions including d structures in advanced devices and scaling to 0 mm wafers with corporate headquarters located in fremont california the company maintains a network of facilities throughout asia north america and europe to meet the complex and changing needs of its global customer base veeco instruments inc  •  semiconductors  •  plainview ny veeco instruments inc designs manufactures and markets equipment for light emitting diodes and hard disk drives as well as concentrator photovoltaics power semiconductors wireless components and microelectromechanical systems the company was founded in  and is headquartered in plainview ny screen holdings co ltd  •  semiconductors  •  kyoto ky screen holdings co ltd engages in the management of its group companies that manufactures and sells semiconductors and printing equipment it operates through the following segments semiconductor equipment se flat panel display equipment fe media and precision technology mp and others the se segment develops and manufactures semiconductor production equipment and conducts sales and maintenance services the fe segment develops manufactures and markets fpd production equipment and it also conducts maintenance services the mp segment develops manufactures sells and maintains graphic arts equipment and pcb related equipment  the others